rComments: This class was ridiculous.  The notes on the test make you think that you're going to be set, but they don't help.  Exams are impossible (minus the first one).  Half of the questions on the exam you can't even understand.  DO NOT TAKE THIS CLASS WITH PERRY!!

Worst class I have ever had. He lets you use his notes on the test but they are not helpful at all. First test was really easy but the second two tests were impossible do not take him other teachers are far easier!
Class wasn't really all that hard, especially if you use the lecture videos posted online to study. I never paid attention during lecture and still got an A.
